Primary Flow 
	1. User is redirected to the employees page
	2. User selects an employee to promote.
	3. User assigns admin role to select user
	4. System updates the employee's role and access permissions accordingly.

Alternate Flow(s)

DEMOTION FAILURE
b1 - User attempts to demote a manager who is the only supervisor for an active group.
b2 - System prevents the demotion and prompts the user to assign a new manager first.